snippet.title: Jamai Raja (HD) - Hindi Full Movie - Anil Kapoor, Madhuri Dixit - Hit Movie - (With Eng Subtitles)
snippet.description:
A shrewd entrepreneur, Durgeshwari Devi, manages her business with an iron hand. She shows little emotions and is often cruel in matters that affect her honor. She sends a poor girl Indu to Jail on false charges when Indu refuses to break up with her son Dheeraj. Outraged by her actions, Indu's brother Raja, promises to seek revenge. He marries his lover Rekha, after learning that she is Durgeshwari's daughter. Raja then draws a plan to teach Durgeshwari an unforgettable lesson on humility.
